metadata.name: Beautiful enchanting
metadata.description:
"Master Zhang, is this the only broken sword you want?"



Qin Ya walks past to Zhang Ruochen, plump jiao body almost stands with him close-fitting together, the body sends out attractive fragrance.



Zhang Ruochen returns to god gradually from in the feeling of preexistence, just look up, the white skin that sees qin Ya shows before the bosom is large, although lie between unlined upper garment, appear as before however very sweet and colourful.



Zhang Ruochen's eyes froze, slightly suffocated, and his heart beat wildly. He immediately pinched his finger tips and forcibly moved his eyes to stare at the sword hanging on the wall.
